SEARCH
Package com.example.donotredeem

Class SearchedUserTest

java.lang.Object
com.example.donotredeem.SearchedUserFragmentTest
public class SearchedUserTest extends Object
Unit tests for the SearchedUser fragment's date/time parsing and mood event sorting functionality. Verifies correct handling of various input formats and proper chronological ordering of events.

Test scenarios include:

  • Valid and invalid date parsing scenarios
  • Time parsing with/without seconds and boundary cases
  • Chronological sorting of mood events (date descending, then time descending)

Uses reflection to access private fields and includes a mock MoodEvent implementation for testing.
